cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper focuses on model-based reinforcement learning using probabilistic graphical models to learn representations for inferring dynamics from real-world rollouts. This involves techniques from machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, and cs.SY, in that order.
